textAnnotations.description:
A SIP OF CONFLICT
The water in this drinking fountain is
erfectly clean, and the toilet has newer
bean used. So why do people often
hesitate before taking a drink?
Strong emotional associations with
objects or people can make it difficult
to act rationaly around them.
